flowchart TD

A[User Query] --> B[Query Planning Agent]

B --> C[Decompose Query + Identify Intent]

C --> D[Parallel Retrieval Agents]

D --> E[ANN Search (Chunks + Summaries)]
E --> F[Section Ranking (Support-based)]

F --> G[Context Assembly]

G --> H[Context Filtering Agent]
H --> I[Query Augmentation Agent]

I --> J[LLM Reasoning]

J --> K{More Context Needed?}
K -- Yes --> D
K -- No --> L{Context Sufficient?}

L -- No --> M[Fallback Answer (Explain)]
L -- Yes --> N[Grounded Answer]

M --> O[Final Response + Assets + Traceability]
N --> O

